participant "OSOKServiceManager" as ServiceManager
participant OCI
note over BaseReconciler,ServiceManager
shared resolution:
shared/diagrams/shared-resolution-sequence.svg
shared delete:
shared/diagrams/shared-delete-sequence.svg
end note
Kubernetes -> Controller: enqueue Assessment reconcile
Controller -> BaseReconciler: Reconcile(request)
BaseReconciler -> ServiceManager: reconcile desired Assessment
group Lookup and bind
alt tracked or explicit OCI identity already exists
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetAssessment
else tracked identity is missing
ServiceManager -> OCI: ListAssessments(filters:\ncompartment_id, display_name,\nlifecycle_details, lifecycle_state)
alt reusable OCI resource is not found
ServiceManager -> OCI: CreateAssessment
loop create pending CREATING, IN_PROGRESS
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetAssessment
end
else reusable OCI resource already exists
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetAssessment
end
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: persist resolved OCI identity in status
end
alt delete requested
group Delete
ServiceManager -> OCI: DeleteAssessment
ServiceManager -> OCI: confirm delete via GetAssessment or\nListAssessments
loop delete pending DELETING
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetAssessment or ListAssessments
end
alt cleanup or finalizer release is blocked
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: retain delete state and retry
else delete completion observed
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: release finalizer after delete completion
end
end
else OCI state is retryable
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: requeue while OCI remains in\nCREATING, IN_PROGRESS, UPDATING,\nDELETING
else live state requires field-aware\ndrift evaluation
group Drift handling
note over ServiceManager,OCI
Supported update surface:
acceptable_downtime, creation_type,
database_data_size, ddl_expectation (+7
more)
Reject before mutate: force-new fields
bulk_include_exclude_data,
compartment_id, database_combination,
exclude_objects (+1 more)
Lookup filters: compartment_id,
display_name, lifecycle_details,
lifecycle_state
end note
opt force-new or conflicting drift is detected
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: reject before OCI mutation
end
opt supported mutable drift is detected
ServiceManager -> OCI: Apply UpdateAssessment only for\nmutable fields acceptable_downtime,\ncreation_type, database_data_size,\nddl_expectation (+7 more)
loop update pending UPDATING, IN_PROGRESS
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetAssessment
end
end
ServiceManager -> OCI: run helper hooks\ncreate=tfresource.CreateResource,\ntfresource.WaitForWorkRequestWithErrorHandling\nentity=assessment action=CREATED;\nupdate=tfresource.UpdateResource,\ntfresource.WaitForWorkRequestWithErrorHandling\nentity=assessment action=UPDATED;\ndelete=tfresource.DeleteResource,\ntfresource.WaitForWorkRequestWithErrorHandling\nentity=assessment action=DELETED
end
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: status=required,\nfinalizer=retain-until-confirmed-delete
end
BaseReconciler --> Controller: requeue on provisioning, updating,\nterminating
note right of ServiceManager
shared diagram:
shared/diagrams/shared-resolution-sequence.svg
shared delete diagram:
shared/diagrams/shared-delete-sequence.svg
